{"tid":2112543,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[IT]微軟傳7月以來全球裁員 或涉最多1000人","createTime":"2020-07-17T11:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T01:38:13.000Z","uid":225931,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"42d2fb333b23a2abecd2faf649f5672ca70216b1","tid":2112543,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2695000/2698672/MSFT_v1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2695000%2F2698672%2FMSFT_v1_1024.jpg&h=ef0cf6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n微軟自7月踏入新財年以來，在全球不同地區和團隊都進行了裁員。微軟拒絕透露裁員涉及的職位、人數以及地區。<br />\n<br />\n外媒早前報道，微軟在本周裁減最多1000個職位，<a href=\"http://包括其線上新聞網站MSN.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%85%B6%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99MSN.com&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=e8f1a0a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">包括其線上新聞網站MSN.com</a>，轉向依靠AI（人工智能）算法進行推送，此外雲業務部門Azure也在裁員範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n微軟上月宣佈，因新冠肺炎疫情持續，永久關閉所有實體零售店鋪，並預計會產生4.5億美元的稅前費用。<br />\n<br />\n微軟發言人則稱，進入新財年後，公司重新審視評估其業務是正常的。"},{"pid":"a1e2b44072e45d2cce34af029df726ef846adbac","tid":2112543,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:48:56.000Z","msg":"唔係話IT吃香咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6fd01b7af6ee61049d709d6ef684b9befc073ca","tid":2112543,"uid":23699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:21:33.000Z","msg":"又炒 QA <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8483b781edec3d7c68af97e4656cfd4461f6ffca","tid":2112543,"uid":39503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a1e2b44072e45d2cce34af029df726ef846adbac","tid":2112543,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11: